OL,3,CMenopause questions in NHS health
OL,4,Cchecks to stop women 'suffering in
OL,5,Csilence'
OL,7,FQuestions about the menopause will be
OL,8,Fincluded in NHS health checks for the
OL,9,Ffirst time, officials have announced,
OL,10,Fin a move that could benefit millions
OL,11,Fof women in England.
OL,13,FHealth Secretary Wes Streeting said
OL,14,Fwomen have been "suffering in silence
OL,15,Ffor too long" and the update will give
OL,16,Fthose experiencing symptoms such as
OL,17,Fhot flushes, mood swings and trouble
OL,18,Fsleeping "visibility and support".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
