OL,7,FTheir aim is to detect people at risk
OL,8,Fof developing conditions such as heart
OL,9,Fand kidney disease, type 2 diabetes,
OL,10,Fdementia and stroke.
OL,12,FThe inclusion of questions about
OL,13,Fmenopause will aim to raise awareness
OL,14,Fabout symptoms and also give women
OL,15,Fconfidence to seek help, officials
OL,16,Fsaid.
OL,18,FSpecific questions will be developed
OL,19,Fover the coming months, with guidance
OL,20,Ffrom health experts.
