OL,7,FThe addition could benefit almost five
OL,8,Fmillion women, the Department of
OL,9,FHealth and Social Care (DHSC)
OL,10,Festimates.
OL,12,F"Women have been suffering in silence
OL,13,Ffor far too long and haven't been
OL,14,Fencouraged to open up about the
OL,15,Fsymptoms they're experiencing,"
OL,16,FStreeting said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
