OL,7,F"This often means they're left to
OL,8,Fnavigate menopause alone, with very
OL,9,Flittle support - all because of an
OL,10,Foutdated health system that fails to
OL,11,Facknowledge how serious it can be.
OL,13,F"No one should have to grit their
OL,14,Fteeth and just get on with what can be
OL,15,Fdebilitating symptoms or be told that
OL,16,Fit's simply part of life.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
