OL,7,F"This government is overhauling
OL,8,Fwomen's healthcare and giving those
OL,9,Fexperiencing menopause and
OL,10,Fperimenopause the visibility and
OL,11,Fsupport they have long been asking
OL,12,Ffor."
OL,14,FHormone replacement therapy (HRT),
OL,15,Fwhich replaces the hormones that are
OL,16,Fat low levels, is the main treatment
OL,17,Ffor menopause.
OL,19,FOther medicines can help with specific
OL,20,Fsymptoms like hot flushes and mood
OL,21,Fswings.
