OL,7,FIt is estimated that three-quarters of
OL,8,Fwomen have symptoms such as weigh
OL,9,Fgain, joint pain, memory issues and
OL,10,Fbrain fog.
OL,12,FHowever, according to DHSC, fewer than
OL,13,Fone in ten feel they have enough
OL,14,Finformation to cope with the changes.
