OL,7,FDr Sue Mann, national clinical
OL,8,Fdirector in women's health at NHS
OL,9,FEngland, said: "Far too often we still
OL,10,Fhear women say their concerns aren't
OL,11,Flistened to or that they aren't
OL,12,Fgetting enough support for the
OL,13,Fdebilitating symptoms that can come
OL,14,Fwith the menopause, many of which can
OL,15,Fhave a big impact on their lives and
OL,16,Fcan be invisible to others.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
