OL,7,F"We want to change that - no-one
OL,8,Fshould have to put on a brave face or
OL,9,Ffeel they are facing symptoms of
OL,10,Fmenopause or perimenopause on their
OL,11,Fown.
OL,13,F"By tailoring NHS health checks to
OL,14,Finclude questions around menopause, we
OL,15,Fhope more women will get the support
OL,16,Fthey need to manage their symptoms -
OL,17,Fand this is testament to our ongoing
OL,18,Fcommitment to improving treatment,
OL,19,Fcare and quality of life for women."
